Pokažite mu.

922
01:31:53,904 --> 01:31:56,130
Reci "Ah".

923
01:32:15,881 --> 01:32:18,693
Vrlo dobro. Vrlo dobro.

924
01:32:18,785 --> 01:32:20,882
Ovdje je puno novca za mene.

925
01:32:20,976 --> 01:32:23,322
Evkuacija!

926
01:32:26,152 --> 01:32:28,044
Za njima!

